description: Farm to Fender specializes in locally sourced healthy fare. Our food is full of healthy energy that has been produced in a sustainable way. We offer healthy-gluten free, vegetarian, and vegan meals! The specials lean towards the carnivores with southern favorites that really stick to your bones.  We also offer a kids menu to keep the little ones healthy and happy. We cook with the season and work with over 15 local farmers, supporting our local economy and creating a stronger community.
name: Farm To Fender
